CustomField.description: 5-digit code associated with the CBSA for this location. For CBSA's containing Metropolitan Divisions, GeoResults recognizes the Metro Division Code in place of the CBSA Code. This substitution is meant to provide more efficient analysis within exceptionally large geographies.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: 5-digit code associated with the CBSA for this location.
CustomField.label: CBSA Code
